data.description: $40,000 PRICE CUT FOR DECEMBER ONLY! Spectacular custom built home in Wind Wood Estates!. A lot can be said about this beautiful home, but the pictures say it all. Custom Home builder Cam Suggs, owner of ACS Home Builders, pays particular attention to quality and detail, which resonate throughout the home. Two massive fireplaces of stone and granite accentuate the open floor plan, which offers private get-away spaces that have become popular for the post-covid work from home professional. Two bedrooms down and 2 bedrooms up. Just far enough from Nashville that you can unwind while living among farms, horses and pastureland. Nothing about this home will disappoint you.
